{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "c8f4b2e5-6a39-4dba-9c7f-2e4a6b8d0f3c",
		"name": "Smart Redact Orchestrator API",
		"description": "API collection for the Smart Redact Orchestrator Service.\n\n## Authentication Flow\n\n1. **Login** -- `POST /v1/auth/login` with default credentials (`admin` / `Admin1234`). The access token is saved automatically.\n2. **Reset Password (first login)** -- `POST /v1/auth/reset-password` with a new password. Required on first login.\n3. **Use protected endpoints** -- The `{{accessToken}}` variable is set in the Authorization header automatically.\n4. **Refresh** -- `POST /v1/auth/refresh` when the access token expires (15 min). Uses the HttpOnly refresh cookie.\n5. **Logout** -- `POST /v1/auth/logout` to invalidate the refresh token.\n\n## Default Credentials\n\n- **Login:** `admin`\n- **Password:** `Admin1234`\n\nYou will be prompted to reset the password on first login.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Saved accessToken (expires: \" + jsonData.expiresAt + \")\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"login\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"Admin1234\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"v1",
								"auth",
								"login"
							]
						},
						"description": "Authenticates a user and returns an access token. Sets an HttpOnly refresh token cookie.\n\nOn first login with default credentials, the token will contain a `password_reset_required` claim -- call **Reset Password** next.\n\nThe access token is automatically saved to `{{accessToken}}`."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Reset Password (First Login)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Password reset successful. Saved new accessToken.\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"newPassword\": \"MySecurePassword1!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/reset-password",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"v1",
								"auth",
								"reset-password"
							]
						},
						"description": "Resets the password for a user whose JWT token has the `password_reset_required` claim set to true. Required on first login with default credentials.\n\nReturns 403 if the claim is not present. The new access token is automatically saved to `{{accessToken}}`."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Change Password",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Password changed. Saved new accessToken.\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"currentPassword\": \"MySecurePassword1!\",\n    \"newPassword\": \"NewPassword1!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/change-password",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"v1",
								"auth",
								"change-password"
							]
						},
						"description": "Changes the password for the currently authenticated user. All existing refresh tokens are revoked. The new access token is automatically saved to `{{accessToken}}`."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Refresh Token",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Token refreshed. Saved new accessToken (expires: \" + jsonData.expiresAt + \")\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/refresh",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"v1",
								"auth",
								"refresh"
							]
						},
						"description": "Issues a new access token using the refresh token from the HttpOnly cookie. The refresh token is rotated on every use.\n\nNo Authorization header needed -- uses the cookie set by Login. The new access token is automatically saved to `{{accessToken}}`."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Logout",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"accessToken\", \"\");",
									"    console.log(\"Logged out. Cleared accessToken.\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/logout",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"v1",
								"auth",
								"logout"
							]
						},
						"description": "Logs out the current user by invalidating all refresh tokens and clearing the cookie. The `{{accessToken}}` variable is cleared automatically."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Authentication endpoints. Start with **Login**, then **Reset Password** on first login. See collection description for the full flow."
		},
